name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, ex rel, Eugene CARVALHO, Petitioner, v. Judge WEIST, John Broda, and Da Anthony Rosini, Respondents
name_abbreviation: Commonwealth ex rel. Carvalho v. Weist

parties: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, ex rel, Eugene CARVALHO, Petitioner, v. Judge WEIST, John Broda, and Da Anthony Rosini, Respondents.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 26th day of June, 2007, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is granted. The Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus is denied and the Judge’s name is to be stricken from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
